thread.title_full: Peaches Boutique reviewed by Greta Urban

author: Greta Urban
title: Greta Urban
text: Maria G was my consultant and she helped me so much. She kept me calm when I felt pressure from my family and she found every dress I wanted. She didn't make me feel rushed at all. I would not have been able to find my dress without her. Thank you Maria I miss you!!!!
